            "description": "Creates a valid BUY signal for BTCUSDT.\n\n**BUY Rules Applied:**\n- stop_loss (85000) < entry_price (90000) ✅\n- target_price (95000) > entry_price (90000) ✅\n- expiry_time is after entry_time ✅\n\n**Expected Response:** 201 Created"
